OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers near
OL,6,Fsouthern and western coasts overnight,
OL,7,Fbut becoming dry inland with clear
OL,8,Fspells. Turning chilly with a rural
OL,9,Fgrass frost. The odd fog patch forming
OL,10,Fin the lighter winds too.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FMonday should start mostly
OL,13,Ffine with some sunshine. However,
OL,14,Fshowers will break out during the day,
OL,15,Fturning locally heavy and thundery.
OL,16,FFeeling less chilly than recently with
OL,17,Fgentle winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
