OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fbright start for most on Tuesday then
OL,7,Fturning cloudier from the west with
OL,8,Fpatchy rain. Wet and windy on
OL,9,FWednesday, then sunshine and showers
OL,10,Fon Thursday. Temperatures rising
OL,11,Fslightly.
